{"tid":1258523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★派$4000派到一塌糊塗　鄺神 促政府道歉","createTime":"2019-06-26T07:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T07:59:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6404cca0ca6e6ee898dc1e3e6c798391182eebb8","tid":1258523,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:03:39.000Z","msg":"港府為財政預算案補鑊，透過關愛共享計劃向合資格的市民派錢4000港元，但派表和收表過程卻頻頻「甩轆」。財經事務及庫務局局長劉怡翔今午(26日)在立法會上回應議員質詢時，指截至昨日(25日)為止，在職家庭津貼辦事處已向逾61.7萬名成功申請的市民發放款額，並指現時每日可向約2.8萬宗成功申請個案發放款額，最新目標是於今年9月底前完成處理所有申請。<br />\n<br />\n提出質詢的議員<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺俊宇在會上批評，政府「派錢都差唔多派足半年」、「派錢派到一塌糊塗」，形容市民「一肚氣」。</span>他表示，政府的派錢安排混亂，期間更多次傳出職津處有遺失表格事宜、出現離職潮等消息，認為政府應向市民道歉。<br />\n<br />\n議員葉劉淑儀則形容，政府是次派錢是「執漏」，導致派得較為「論盡」，並問及政府會否吸取教訓，日後在有盈餘情況下要「大方啲，一早派」、甚至「人人都係當封利是咁派」，做法會簡單點，政府亦能節省行政費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190626/bkn-20190626134147286-0626_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190626%2Fbkn-20190626134147286-0626_00822_001.html&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=ee0ba468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190626/bkn-20190626134147286-0626_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n劉怡翔表示，每年會根據財政預算、當時的公共財政情況、以及社會訴求去制訂措施。他表示，關愛共享計劃素來是具針對性的措施，在不同地方有寬減措施時或經已受惠時，就不應再有雙重措施。他又指，職津處接獲7000宗個案指未有收到確認申請，當中有一成是沒有收到申請，會容許這些市民補交。"},{"pid":"62b9209902c9e68b42b20bcd6e09c677d5f3c7dd","tid":1258523,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"鄺神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13cbdd549f63b79d7f0ff56a1371a32b477d265","tid":1258523,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>。<br />\n議員葉劉淑儀則形容，政府是次派錢是「執漏」，導致派得較為「論盡」，並問及政府會否吸取教訓，日後在有盈餘情況下要「<span style=\"color: red;\">大方啲，一早派</span>」、甚至「<span style=\"color: red;\">人人都係當封利是咁派</span>」，做法會簡單點，政府亦能節省行政費。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n謬波：仲以為你地已經唔記得咗我添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPS：葉劉又補刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb8bb90ccacd555548ed534551d58d9c822af69","tid":1258523,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4AWpZjn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4AWpZjn.png&h=ee997105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">[size=5]冇暫緩[/siz<br />\ne=5]</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a548e8d8b0f8ffd08f6eb6c7f73c8d3bb8f6b7","tid":1258523,"uid":10806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4bb8bb90ccacd555548ed534551d58d9c822af69","tid":1258523,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4AWpZjn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4AWpZjn.png&h=ee997105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">[size=5]冇暫緩[/siz<br />\ne=5]</span></span><br /